Text:
This contains some of the cream of goa trance... For those who think goa is just psycho shit, well give this a shot.
You may find its actually very well developed and intricate music.
there's a naming error in the torrent. track #29 should be Analog Pussy - Go Wacko and not Analog Pussy - Solipse Technology. Sorry about that, had tracks 2 & 3 from their album mixed up.

Must say, nice collection. Shoulda slipped in some 1200 Micrograms though. ;) haha

Thx for the upload M8
Thanks :) Well 1200Mics is more psy, Israeli full-on style, so it wouldn't really go here.
can anybody point me to Ingmar Veck - Der Zeitfluss? is one of the most powerfull tracks i ever encountered, i have it on casette, but i can't find it anywhere to download it in digital format.
I know what Goa Trance is, but i don't have any. i like listening to it from time to time. love the synths and production skills in the songs. thanks for this, will dl it now. :)
Thanks.....really beginning to get into this genre.
